<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="true">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

有哪些电影一定要趁年轻看？

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2462441" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"><i>（不要刷小时代。）</i></div>


</div>
