</div>


<div class="zm-editable-content clearfix">
<p>《横道世之介》</p><p>你会如何回忆我 带着笑或是很沉默</p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/4ad5aa930e65e46640e720f3b6da0e59_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="1364" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/4ad5aa930e65e46640e720f3b6da0e59_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="1364" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/4ad5aa930e65e46640e720f3b6da0e59_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/4ad5aa930e65e46640e720f3b6da0e59_b.png"><p>这部电影是一个朋友向我推荐的。他说，《横道世之介》在他看过的所有青春片中，可以排top1。他还说，他很想成为世之介这样的人，在朋友提起他的名字时会觉得认识他是件幸运的事。<br><br>这应该是所有看完这部电影的人都会有的感受。我们都有这样的小私心，希望身边人日后回忆起自己时，是带着笑的。<br><br><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/24d500d3a927f759879b128c37898307_b.png" data-rawwidth="320" data-rawheight="201" class="content_image" width="320"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="320" data-rawheight="201" class="content_image lazy" width="320" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/24d500d3a927f759879b128c37898307_b.png"><br>《横道世之介》是一部小人物传记电影，讲述了上世纪八十年代，出生在长崎港口小镇的18岁男孩横道世之介，前往东京开始新的学业和人生旅程，并在那里和富家千金谢野祥子展开的爱情故事和他身边人的青春物语。<br><br>横道世之介并不是主角，他只是你身边的一个普通男同学，蠢蠢的，讲话总是慢半拍；拘谨，总是勾着腰；很善良，会力所能及地帮助你，给你带来欢乐。<br><br><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/bbf08233afa08193ead67cd77c4bb478_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/bbf08233afa08193ead67cd77c4bb478_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/bbf08233afa08193ead67cd77c4bb478_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/bbf08233afa08193ead67cd77c4bb478_b.png"></p><br><p>影片通过世之介大学时认识的几个好朋友对他的回忆展开了叙事。这些朋友早已和世之介断了联系，但因为生活中遇到的一些事触发他们又重新回忆起大学时认识的世之介这样一个人，还有和他一起经历的青春成长。<br><br>每个人生命里都会有这样一些过客，我们互相陪伴走过人生中的一小段，后来又因为这啊那的原因走丢了。或许是因为闹了点小矛盾；或许是日后再无交集；或许是生活所迫，大家都忙着生计。可是日后想起时仍怀抱善意——噢，她啊，是我初中时玩得还蛮好的朋友，虽然现在没什么联系了，可当时很喜欢和她一起玩，不知道现在过得怎么样了。<br><br>世之介也是他们的过客。导演并没有向我们交待，他们后来是如何断了联系，也没交待分别后各自的生活是怎样的，因为这些，都不重要。</p><br><p>日后回忆起你，语焉不详，这就是真实的生活本身。<br><br>世之介到底是一个什么样的人呢？影片开头我们都很好奇，但其实，他只是如你我一般的普通人。</p><br><p><strong>▼</strong></p><p><strong>打工收到额外的小费很开心</strong></p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/91c8c2df3e93096b2dcb4fbcd822ed32_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/91c8c2df3e93096b2dcb4fbcd822ed32_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/91c8c2df3e93096b2dcb4fbcd822ed32_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/91c8c2df3e93096b2dcb4fbcd822ed32_b.png"><p><br><strong>▼</strong></p><p><strong>八卦好友的感情故事</strong></p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c6083bd5a6909635f7b214fa5876e9a3_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c6083bd5a6909635f7b214fa5876e9a3_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c6083bd5a6909635f7b214fa5876e9a3_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c6083bd5a6909635f7b214fa5876e9a3_b.png"><br><p><strong>▼</strong></p><p><strong>看见美女也会忍不住盯着看</strong></p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a36b2faa05a7cf3bae21932922fab651_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a36b2faa05a7cf3bae21932922fab651_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a36b2faa05a7cf3bae21932922fab651_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a36b2faa05a7cf3bae21932922fab651_b.png"><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a1daec0b7f58f8ff2aa1002d2382ef39_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a1daec0b7f58f8ff2aa1002d2382ef39_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a1daec0b7f58f8ff2aa1002d2382ef39_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a1daec0b7f58f8ff2aa1002d2382ef39_b.png"><br><p><strong>▼</strong></p><p><strong>一边吃泡面一边用筷子翻书</strong></p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/c5687ebcf0a1d24548cb54bbb1080dcd_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/c5687ebcf0a1d24548cb54bbb1080dcd_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/c5687ebcf0a1d24548cb54bbb1080dcd_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/c5687ebcf0a1d24548cb54bbb1080dcd_b.png"><br><p><strong>▼</strong></p><p><strong>好友出柜后 很忐忑</strong></p><p><strong>告诉他如果介意的话以后可以不用再见</strong></p><p><strong>他第一反应却是以为对方不想让自己去他家吹空调吃西瓜了</strong></p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/ae79536b64fad4d2ebe59c8a251ca69a_b.png" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/ae79536b64fad4d2ebe59c8a251ca69a_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/ae79536b64fad4d2ebe59c8a251ca69a_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/ae79536b64fad4d2ebe59c8a251ca69a_b.png"><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c0dc56c0dc4ff6f76f5b5854eff45fda_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c0dc56c0dc4ff6f76f5b5854eff45fda_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c0dc56c0dc4ff6f76f5b5854eff45fda_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c0dc56c0dc4ff6f76f5b5854eff45fda_b.png"><br><p><strong>▼</strong></p><p><strong>第一次接吻时的羞涩</strong><br></p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/e024dafbbc3289790fe46d93624bb9b6_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/e024dafbbc3289790fe46d93624bb9b6_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/e024dafbbc3289790fe46d93624bb9b6_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/e024dafbbc3289790fe46d93624bb9b6_b.png"><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/89758ba7a1199b27c88232e0fff65cd6_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/89758ba7a1199b27c88232e0fff65cd6_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/89758ba7a1199b27c88232e0fff65cd6_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/89758ba7a1199b27c88232e0fff65cd6_b.png"><br><p><strong>▼</strong></p><p><strong>担心女友</strong></p><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/beddf79ea5c6f43ae4db4b339196f0ab_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/beddf79ea5c6f43ae4db4b339196f0ab_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/beddf79ea5c6f43ae4db4b339196f0ab_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/beddf79ea5c6f43ae4db4b339196f0ab_b.png"><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/ce82d96dedb74bd5f62d8d4fef79d1eb_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/ce82d96dedb74bd5f62d8d4fef79d1eb_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/ce82d96dedb74bd5f62d8d4fef79d1eb_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/ce82d96dedb74bd5f62d8d4fef79d1eb_b.png"><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/7bbcb715fba065dd49da08acd4cb8a4a_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/7bbcb715fba065dd49da08acd4cb8a4a_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/7bbcb715fba065dd49da08acd4cb8a4a_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/7bbcb715fba065dd49da08acd4cb8a4a_b.png"><br>可是这样一个普通人，他的好友和恋人对他的评价却都相当的高。<br><br><br><br><p><strong>▼</strong></p><p><strong>出柜好友加藤认为认识横道很幸运</strong><br></p><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/7075a90d40c0a991f17c6dde51e1b890_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="1586" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/7075a90d40c0a991f17c6dde51e1b890_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="1586" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/7075a90d40c0a991f17c6dde51e1b890_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/7075a90d40c0a991f17c6dde51e1b890_b.png"><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/4d73e8cf798be43e765b1788e5318ab7_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="1102" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/4d73e8cf798be43e765b1788e5318ab7_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="1102" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/4d73e8cf798be43e765b1788e5318ab7_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/4d73e8cf798be43e765b1788e5318ab7_b.png"><br><p><strong>▼</strong></p><p><strong>初恋女友的评价</strong><br></p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/f57b1de7c44da78f8740fab72abbc95c_b.png" data-rawwidth="681" data-rawheight="1824" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="681" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/f57b1de7c44da78f8740fab72abbc95c_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="681" data-rawheight="1824" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="681" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/f57b1de7c44da78f8740fab72abbc95c_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/f57b1de7c44da78f8740fab72abbc95c_b.png"><br><p><strong>▼</strong></p><p><strong>好友仓持搬家时也只想到能找他帮忙</strong><br></p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/ab1d9953311a7aecd89d5e6f3d73040d_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/ab1d9953311a7aecd89d5e6f3d73040d_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/ab1d9953311a7aecd89d5e6f3d73040d_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/ab1d9953311a7aecd89d5e6f3d73040d_b.png"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/de55bdc37dd88bb64cff9e58e515b934_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/de55bdc37dd88bb64cff9e58e515b934_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/de55bdc37dd88bb64cff9e58e515b934_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/de55bdc37dd88bb64cff9e58e515b934_b.png"><br><p><strong>▼</strong></p><p><strong>大学时的女友说他就是个普通得让人发笑的人</strong><br></p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/71d65c0c4f2179885d62da545fd3fb67_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/71d65c0c4f2179885d62da545fd3fb67_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/71d65c0c4f2179885d62da545fd3fb67_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/71d65c0c4f2179885d62da545fd3fb67_b.png"><br><p>▼<br></p><p><strong>母亲也说 有世之介这个儿子 很幸福</strong></p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/2d6297bc59ab1c144bf664864231af3a_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/2d6297bc59ab1c144bf664864231af3a_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="554" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/2d6297bc59ab1c144bf664864231af3a_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/2d6297bc59ab1c144bf664864231af3a_b.png"><br><p>世之介单纯、善良、又温暖，是个普普通通在青春里遇到可能马上就又忘了的人。他是我们生活中的配角，可能在记忆中早已模糊了面孔，可忽然某日，一件不经意的小事，我们将他重新想起，人人都难掩嘴角的笑意和由衷产生的幸福感。</p><br><p>​<br></p><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c3075a63069930401dab2c73f95d1c22_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="656" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c3075a63069930401dab2c73f95d1c22_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="656" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c3075a63069930401dab2c73f95d1c22_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c3075a63069930401dab2c73f95d1c22_b.png"><br><p>正是这一个个过客，构成了我们的过去，也让我们成为了现在的自己。我们也曾是或正是他人生命中的过客。而成为像世之介一样的普通人，我们每个人，都可以做到！</p><br><br><br><p>若他日在你回忆里经过，该是怎样的面容。</p><br><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c974db5a64caed0b6cdeb58a15f0566a_b.png" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="1586" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c974db5a64caed0b6cdeb58a15f0566a_r.png"></noscript><img src="//zhstatic.zhihu.com/assets/zhihu/ztext/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="984" data-rawheight="1586" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="984" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c974db5a64caed0b6cdeb58a15f0566a_r.png" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c974db5a64caed0b6cdeb58a15f0566a_b.png">
</div>


</div>
